    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You attack with magically-empowered gauntlets.</p>\n<details>\n<summary style=\"padding-bottom:8px\"><strong>Full Description</strong></summary>\n<blockquote style=\"font-style:normal\">\n<p>While wearing the gauntlets, increase your walking speed by 5 feet.</p>\n<p>These gauntlets can be thrown magically. Doing so, a gauntlet detaches and flies at the attack's target, then immediately returns to the wearer and reattaches.</p>\n<p>These gauntlets can't be removed against the wearer's will.</p>\n<p>If the wearer is missing any limbs, the armor replaces those limbs - hands, arms, feet, legs, or similar appendages. The replacements function identically to the body parts they replace.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</details>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p><em>Note: These gauntlets are from the Artificer's @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-class-features.hEpK0xpPbrPPqAwE]{Arcane Propulsion Armor} feature.</em></p>\n</section>",
